reviews.review_text:
Fantastic Bertha I knew that someone had to have a better quality then what has previously been here for all these years. To me the other 2 versions are muddy and distant. This captures this night better then the other 2.  Just check out Phil on bertha he throws out the booming bash towards the end . Plus can hear cymbals on this one. 
 Am sure those of us who were on this tour have also wanted a better version .  
The security at this show was rather tough on us they were thrown out head's for dancing in my section of the floor.  Only a short way into this but I like it. 4 stars because I hope others check it out asap
